    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcription" xml:lang="es">
                <div type="textpart" subtype="envelope">
                  <p><expan><abbr>Il</abbr><ex>ustrísi</ex><abbr>mo</abbr><am>.</am></expan> <expan><abbr>S</abbr><ex>ignor</ex><abbr>r</abbr><am>.</am></expan> <persName ref="#EM">Ernesto Monaci</persName>, professore dell’<orgName ref="#Sapienza">Università Romana</orgName>.
                        <address><addrLine>Piazza della Chiesa </addrLine> 
                            <addrLine>Nuova. <placeName ref="#roma">ROMA</placeName></addrLine></address> </p> 
                <div type="textpart" subtype="letter">
                    <opener> <expan><abbr>S</abbr><ex>eño</ex><abbr>r</abbr><am>.</am></expan> <expan><abbr>D</abbr><am>.</am><ex>on</ex></expan> <persName ref="#EM">Ernesto Monaci</persName>.
                        <salute>Muy <expan><abbr>S</abbr><ex>eño</ex><abbr>r</abbr><am>.</am></expan> Mio y amigo:</salute></opener>
                    
                        
                    <p>Remito a <expan><abbr>U</abbr><ex>ste</ex><abbr>d</abbr><am>.</am></expan> por el correo las fotografías 
                        del <title ref="#poemacid"><hi rend="underline">Poema del Cid</hi></title>, suplicandole 
                        <expan><abbr>q</abbr><am>.</am><ex>u</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> me perdone las dilaciones <expan><abbr>q</abbr><am>.</am><ex>u</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> éste asunto ha tenido, sin culpa mia.</p>
                        <p> Celebraré <expan><abbr>q</abbr><am>.</am><ex>u</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> hayan quedado a satisfaccion de <expan><abbr>U</abbr><ex>ste</ex><abbr>d</abbr><am>.</am></expan> El fotógrafo conserva los cristales.
                        
                    </p>
                    <closer><salute>De <expan><abbr>U</abbr><ex>ste</ex><abbr>d</abbr><am>.</am></expan> siempre <expan><abbr>af</abbr><ex>ectísi</ex><abbr>mo</abbr><am>.</am></expan>
                        <expan><abbr>am</abbr><am>.</am><ex>ig</ex><abbr>o</abbr></expan> y <expan><abbr>comp</abbr><am>.</am><ex>añer</ex><abbr>o</abbr></expan> <expan><abbr>q</abbr><am>.</am><ex>ue</ex> <abbr>s</abbr><am>.</am><ex>u</ex> <abbr>m</abbr><am>.</am><ex>ano</ex> <abbr>b</abbr><am>.</am><ex>esa</ex></expan></salute>
                        
                        <signed><persName ref="#MMP"><expan><abbr>M</abbr><am>.</am><ex>arcelino</ex></expan> Menéndez y Pelayo</persName></signed></closer>
